      "side": 1,
      "message": "This timeout mechanism is fragile in the CI. Since all interfaces share a single timeout, there is no way to determine if the capture that timed out was the instigator in the overall timeout failure.",
      "revId": "17ab012a809206a32efdc293271b1964e212065c",
      "serverId": "6d2eb258-4fe2-443e-8a38-ca81da23d4c2"
